Anonymous Tue 12 Oct 2021 04:08:09 No.42320502 Report
Quoted By: >>42320537 >>42320738 >>42322239
>>42320451
Here is the basic premise:

In this universe evolution was going the same way it was IRL, with humans slowly becoming the dominant species of the planet, everything was normal until the point where the first sedentary cultures popped up, when history was beginning to be documented though cave paintings. Then an extraordinary and seemingly unexplainable event happened that caused most mammals to abruptly evolve and adopt humanoid features.

It was then that humanity's dominancy was taken from them. With many species' intellect evolving at such accelerated rate, humans began to be out-competed and slowly losing their place at the top of the food chain, sometimes even hunted down due to them being an easier prey than other herbivores that used their new found intelligence alongside their natural abilities to avoid predators.

That doesn't mean humanity just gave up let itself become extinct, their intellect was pushed to new limits with the sudden appearance of competition; they were already highly adaptable and learned really fast from experience or knowledge passed on to them, so they compensated their lack of physical strength with better intelligence and tool crafting (after all why would the anthros bother with tools when they already have them integrated, also manipulation of tools is difficult with paws or hooves),
And thus humanity just became a really small percentage of the population. Still smart and adaptable but out-competed in physical prowess.

>>42320502
In modern times humans often live in secluded communities, as far away from anthros as possible can, this has made a lot of humans really xenophobic; causing a lot of tensions between species. Despite that, they are well regarded by their intelligence and a lot of the most prominent intellectuals in history were human.

The primitive humans of that time barely managed to document those times with abstract cave paintings that depict an event that no one has deciphered what exactly it was, despite being such a crucial event in natural history. This has led some people to believe that the anthros came from a rift in time and space, were they then proceeded to replace all of their primitive counterparts.
It is only in recent times that the scientists discovered barely legible traces of an ancient type of radiation that is now theorized to have existed in many places around the globe, especially in areas that are speculated to be where the first sentient anthro tribes started. This might be a clue to discover once and for all what happen during those primitive times.

It was also recently discovered by a mining corporation that was doing an excavation in Africa, hundreds of meters below earth's surface, a strange element that emits this specific kind of radiation, that, in higher concentrations causes sudden mutations in both anthros and humans; with the anthros getting the worst ones, causing them to deform and exaggerate their animal traits while losing their sentience, becoming feral and extremely aggressive.

The mutations that the humans suffer are more varied and less predictable, with the only consistent traits being that they
Keep their sentience and always adopt some animal characteristic that are greatly enhanced, making it far superior that the one possessed by the original species it came from (even developing characteristics from other non-mammalian species). Some examples being:

One human female developing a skin type similar to the one present in elephants and rhinos, with the difference being that her skin is almost impervious to all damage.
A male teenager developing the ability to transform his arms into wings (resembling the ones from a bald eagle), his feet into talons and even growing the appropriate size tail feathers. He is also able to carry double his body weight and still be capable to take flight despite that.

This peaked the interest the private conglomeration that the mining corporation is part of; this includes the privately owned Biotech laboratories that studies gene manipulation, and it’s willing to perform experiments on both humans and anthros in order to find a way to exploit this element and its exceptional proprieties.
